Auto-detect text files and perform LF normalization

    text=auto

Source code

*.py text diff=python
*.pyi text diff=python
*.md text diff=markdown
*.txt text
*.json text
*.yaml text
*.yml text
*.toml text
Shell scripts

*.sh text eol=lf
Keep line endings for Windows scripts

*.bat text eol=crlf
Binary files

*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary